com.soa.policy.wspolicy

Class PolicyOperator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.soa.policy.wspolicy.PolicyOperator
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    All, ExactlyOne, Policy

    public abstract class PolicyOperator
extends java.lang.Object
    Base class for WS-Policy policy operators. All policy operators can contain other policy operators as well as assertions as children.

      • getPolicyReferences

        public java.util.List<PolicyReference> getPolicyReferences()
        Returns all added policy references. Policy references are typically used at "design time" when modeling policy and not in a runtime environment where references are not useful. Policy operators with policy references cannot be normalized.
        Returns:
        List of PolicyReferences
